Package: spale
Architecture: linux-any
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, ${shlibs:Depends}, systemd
Recommends: bpftool
Description: eBPF Single Packet Authentication with HPKE sender-auth
 High-performance SPA (port knocking) implemented in eBPF (TC or XDP) with an HPKE
 sender-authenticated UDP control channel.

Package: spale-tools
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, python3, python3-cryptography
Description: client tools for spale SPA
 Python-based client utilities for spale, including key generation and SPA
 sender tools, plus profile management for client configurations.

